# Radio-Streamer

You need:

1) If you're building it on a Raspberry Pi you need Raspberry Pi OS Lite: https://www.raspberrypi.com

2) For other computers you need Debian 13 without a GUI: https://www.debian.org

2) BalenaEtcher (https://www.balena.io/etcher) or 'dd command' to create a bootable USB:
    $diskutil list
    $diskutil umountDisk /dev/diskXX
    $sudo dd bs=1m if=YOUR_OS_IMAGE.img of=/dev/diskXX

4) Wi-Fi antenna (if your computer or Raspberry Pi doesn't have one and you want to use this interface): https://a.co/d/3hMnroM

5) Bluetooth antenna (if your computer or Raspberry Pi doesn't have one and you want to use this interface): 

6) USB stick for Raspberry Pi: https://a.co/d/9WlAjas

7) Turn off cable for Raspberry Pi: / Micro USB: https://a.co/d/9Fj24Pe / USB C: https://a.co/d/g3vTr5e

8) Shutdown button for Raspberry Pi: https://a.co/d/0t1HdAW / https://a.co/d/g9fruqO / https://a.co/d/1JmqQhr


